column2: "Ah, <%me>. You came to see me again? That makes me happy."
"I'm not very good at talking to other people. For some reason it's frightening."
"Philia says I might be suffering some kind of trauma, but I don't know what she means by that."
"But, still if you're here <%me>. Then somehow I feel okay."
"That's why, it's okay. I don't need to remember as long as you're here for me."
